       @Override
       public void onActivityResult(int requestCode, int resultCode, Intent data) {
           super.onActivityResult(requestCode, resultCode, data);
           switch (requestCode) {
               case SELECT_PIC:
                   ContentResolver resolver = getContentResolver();
                   if (resultCode != RESULT_OK) {
                       System.out.println("error result code");
                       return;
                   }
                   if (data == null) {
                       return;
                   }
                   Uri uri = data.getData();
                   Bitmap mBit = null;
                   String s = "";
                   try {
                       mBit = MediaStore.Images.Media.getBitmap(resolver, uri);
                       ByteArrayOutputStream arrOut = new ByteArrayOutputStream();
                       mBit.compress(Bitmap.CompressFormat.JPEG,40,arrOut);

                       byte[] bytes = arrOut.toByteArray();
                       s = Base64.getEncoder().encodeToString(bytes);
                   } catch (IOException e) {
                       e.printStackTrace();
                       return;
                   }
